<h1 id="toc0"><span>这是什么？</span></h1>
<p>这是欢乐基金会主题，为放置在<a href="/lolfoundation-hub-page">欢乐基金会</a>中心内的文章而设计。图标由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3781861); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602037160" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3781861); return false;">EstrellaYoshte</a></span>设计，而馀下工作则由我<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5986843); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5986843&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602037160" alt="Ralliston" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5986843)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5986843); return false;">Ralliston</a></span>负责。</p>
<hr />
<h1 id="toc1"><span>使用方法</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc2"><span>注意：这是一个基于黑色标记笔的主题版式。若你想使用此版式，你还需要导入黑色标记笔版式。<a href="/theme:black-highlighter-theme">点击这里了解更多</a>。</span></h2>
<p>在你的作品开头添加如下语法以应用此版式：</p>
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:theme:lolfoundation]]</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<h1 id="toc3"><span>示例</span></h1>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:250px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/theme:lolfoundation/loltestlogo/medium.jpg" style="width:250px;" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:250px;">
<p>此为图片</p>
</div>
</div>
<p>欢乐极兮哀情多，乐道至乐非常乐。基连岛屿规模壮，金锤玉蓥千金地。会当少见会稽绶，乱家更入乱云层。数数看谁得最多，文章天子文章别。欢极轻将翠袖招，乐莫乐于无事乐。 算密意幽欢，可以平哀乐。万化总归基，家书抵万金。五音兮繁会，柳絮飞撩乱。帘幕无重数，数墨强寻文。<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>为寿一尊欢，已是三堪乐。元圣嗣鸿基，曳紫更腰金。早晚朝元会，柳絮飞撩乱。细从今夜数，秘箓示灵文。</p>
</blockquote>
